<div class="container mt-4">
  <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-12 col-sm-8 col-md-6">
      <div class="card shadow">
        <div class="card-header bg-danger text-light text-center">
          <h3 class="h5 mb-0">Eliminar Tipo de Comercio</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="mb-3">
            &iquest;Est&aacute; seguro que desea eliminar este tipo de comercio y todos los comercios asociado a este tipo?
          </p>

          <div class="mb-3">
            <div><strong>Tipo:</strong> {{commerceType.name}}</div>
            <div><strong>Comercios asociados:</strong> {{commercesCount}}</div>
          </div>

          <div class="d-flex justify-content-end gap-2">
            <a href="/commerceType" class="btn btn-secondary">Cancelar</a>
            <form action="/commerceType/delete/{{commerceType._id}}" method="post">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger">Aceptar</button>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
